Supported Platforms:

Includes more than 200 image processing functions, including blank page detection, scanned document image clean up, medical image enhancement, color correction, noise reduction, edge detection, text and MICR detection, and so much more. Most LEADTOOLS image processing functions support region of interest, so that only a region of an image is processed. Additionally, many of the image processing functions support signed and unsigned image data.

LEADTOOLS also offers other related packages so you can create complete, full-featured imaging applications that include 150+ formats, conversion, viewers, and more. To see all that LEADTOOLS has to offer, go to https://www.leadtools.com
